Sometimes I run script/build and it fails with this error

```
>> SyntaxError: variable @x is undefined in node_modules/settings-view/stylesheets/settings-view.less on line 87, column 13:
>> 86           li:hover .disable-theme {
>> 87             .octicon(x);
>> 88             color: #888;
Warning: Error compiling LESS. Use --force to continue.
```

If I run it again, it will build normally.
